g.title: j2039349525
g.text: I shouldn't have reacted the way I did
Segundo, do you mean what you said?

g.title: j2972883579
g.text: I was making that all up.

g.title: j3531428419
g.text: If it's not mutual you can just tell me, I can take it.

g.title: j1434519434
g.text: I still don't know if "mierda" is a good thing or not...

g.title: j668065720
g.text: Un escuincle like that seem more your type

g.title: j4236179991
g.text: But nono, this isn't a bad conversation

g.title: j374513209
g.text: Trust is something that is very hard for me to give away
And it is the most important thing in a relationship for me
Broken trust is something that cannot be repaired, especially in a situation like this

g.title: j3687858218
g.text: You know how hard it is for me to trust people
And how important trust is for me ¿no?
Well... it's even more important when I get into a relationship with someone

g.title: j2008456003
g.text: You know trust is something that is very hard for me to give
And it is the most important thing in a relationship for me
Broken trust is something that cannot be repaired, especially in a situation like this

g.title: j1171949390
g.text: Because the kind of relationships I like to have tend to hurt, solecito
If you get what I'm saying
Only as much as we want it to
And only as far as you're willing to go
Because this kind of thing takes trust

g.title: j451002645
g.text: And broken trust in a thing like this

g.title: j3209482681
g.text: I'm not saying no, but can I ask...why pain is your thing?

g.title: j1785820410
g.text: Only if we get to take turns now and then...

g.title: j1677875942
g.text: I'm not really into mixing pain and pleasure, sorry.

g.title: j39597591
g.text: Maybe because it's pain that I can control
Versus all the pain I can't

g.title: j1749829537
g.text: Need to know I can trust you first

g.title: j3505156629
g.text: Or maybe because it's something intense
Something sharp that cuts through all the rest of the bullshit I have to deal with day in and day out
I can sink my teeth into it

g.title: j1390847172
g.text: Want to make a terrible mistake with me?

g.title: j1442214610
g.text: It doesn't work without it, solecito

g.title: j1570870064
g.text: I need to think this over, actually. Sorry.

g.title: j1581368479
g.text: Let me know if you change your mind

g.title: j3120742129
g.text: I won't go easy on you
I know you can take it

g.title: j1352555945
g.text: I'll always kiss it better after
